_sText:
V2 of CZtexture. Please assess.

CHANGES:
Expanded map with 2 sidehalls filled with rectangular columns for interesting medium/close range fire-fights.
Added slope to the sewer's bottom and removed barrels.
Added ladders from the sidehalls to the second floor with circular steps uptop.
Replaced crate groupings with large circular columns.
Redesigned the 4 barricades by spawns.
Added additional Spawn points.
Overall brush/texture alignment and map polishing.

Enjoy.
